加拿大的政治体-{zh-hans:制; zh-hant:制; }-为[[君主立宪|君主立宪]]下的[[议会制|议会制]]，并采用三权分立，而[[立法权|立法权]]、[[司法权|司法权]]及[[行政權力|行政权]]均源于[[加拿大君主|加拿大君主]]<ref>{{Cite journal |title=Constitution Act, 1867: Preamble |author=Queen Victoria |url=http://www.solon.org/Constitutions/Canada/English/ca_1867.html |date=1867-03-29 |publisher=Queen's Printer |accessdate=2011-05-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100203024121/http://www.solon.org/Constitutions/Canada/English/ca_1867.html |archivedate=2010-02-03 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.queensu.ca/iigr/conf/ConferenceOnTheCrown/CrownConferencePapers/The_Crown_and_the_Constitutio1.pdf |title=The Crown and the Constitution: Sustaining Democracy? |last=Smith |first=David E |date=2010-06-10 |publisher=Queen's University |accessdate=2011-05-23 |page=6 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5qXvz463C?url=http://www.queensu.ca/iigr/conf/ConferenceOnTheCrown/CrownConferencePapers/The_Crown_and_the_Constitutio1.pdf |archivedate=2010-06-17 |dead-url=yes |periodical=The Crown in Canada: Present Realities and Future Options }}</ref><ref name="MacLeod16">{{Cite book |url=http://canadiancrown.gc.ca/DAMAssetPub/DAM-CRN-jblDmt-dmdJbl/STAGING/texte-text/crnMpls_1336157759317_eng.pdf?WT.contentAuthority=4.4.4 |title=A Crown of Maples |last=MacLeod |first=Kevin S. |publisher=Queen's Printer for Canada |accessdate=2011-05-23 |year=2012 |edition=2nd |page=16 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121110140303/http://canadiancrown.gc.ca/DAMAssetPub/DAM-CRN-jblDmt-dmdJbl/STAGING/texte-text/crnMpls_1336157759317_eng.pdf?WT.contentAuthority=4.4.4 |archivedate=2012-11-10 |deadurl=yes |ref=harv |ISBN=978-0-662-46012-1 }}</ref>。现任君主为女王[[伊丽莎白二世|伊丽莎白二世]]，她同时也是其它15个独立的[[英联邦|英联邦]]国家的君主。由于加拿大女王居住在英国，所以她通常会指派[[加拿大總督|总督]]来代表她行使权力<ref>{{Cite web |title=The Governor General of Canada: Roles and Responsibilities |url=http://gg.ca/document.aspx?id=3 |accessdate=2011-05-23 |publisher=Queen's Printer |archive-date=2018-09-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180915122338/http://gg.ca/document.aspx?id=3 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。皇室成员在政府内的权力十分有限<ref name="MacLeod16" /><ref name="Forseyp1">{{Cite book |url=http://www2.parl.gc.ca/sites/lop/aboutparliament/forsey/PDFs/How_Canadians_Govern_Themselves-6ed.pdf |title=How Canadians Govern Themselves |last=Forsey |first=Eugene |publisher=Queen's Printer |accessdate=2011-05-23 |year=2005 |edition=6th |pages=1, 16, 26 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5vkPPetrW?url=http://www2.parl.gc.ca/sites/lop/aboutparliament/forsey/PDFs/How_Canadians_Govern_Themselves-6ed.pdf |archivedate=2011-01-15 |deadurl=yes |ISBN=978-0-662-39689-5 }}</ref><ref name="Montpetit">{{Cite web |title=House of Commons Procedure and Practice: Parliamentary Institutions |url=http://www.parl.gc.ca/MarleauMontpetit/DocumentViewer.aspx?DocId=1001&Lang=E&Print=2&Sec=Ch01&Seq=5 |accessdate=2011-05-23 |last=Marleau |first=Robert |publisher=Queen's Printer |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110828112251/http://www.parl.gc.ca/MarleauMontpetit/DocumentViewer.aspx?DocId=1001&Lang=E&Print=2&Sec=Ch01&Seq=5 |archivedate=2011-08-28 |last2=Montpetit |first2=Camille |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，实际上国家的行政权是在[[内阁|内阁]]身上，一个成员全是国家部长和一些[[加拿大国会下议院|下议院]]议员并由[[加拿大总理|总理]]带领的委员会<ref>{{Cite web |title=Prime Minister of Canada |url=http://www.pm.gc.ca/eng/pm.asp?featureId=7 |accessdate=2011-05-23 |year=2009 |publisher=Queen's Printer |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100419165938/http://www.pm.gc.ca/eng/pm.asp?featureId=7 |archivedate=2010-04-19 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，但是总督或君主依然会保留着一些实权以在危机时使用<ref name="Forseyp1" />。而为了保持政府的稳定，总督通常会由总理提名<ref>{{Cite book |title=Thinking government: public sector management in Canada |url=https://archive.org/details/thinkinggovernme02ndjohn |last=Johnson |first=David |publisher=University of Toronto Press |year=2006 |edition=2nd |pages=[https://archive.org/details/thinkinggovernme02ndjohn/page/134 134]–135, 149 |ISBN=978-1-55111-779-9}}</ref>。{{Link-en|总理办公室 (加拿大)|Office of the Prime Minister (Canada)|总理办公室}}是政府中最具实权的一个机构，其可以发起立法提案，提名总督、[[省督_(加拿大)|省督]]、上议院议员、联邦最高法院大法官、国营企业以及政府机构的负责人<ref name="Forseyp1" />。

[[File:Cansenate.jpg|thumb]]內的[[加拿大国会上议院|上议院]]]]
加拿大的下议院议员是由选民在多個單議席选区中选出，而[[选举|全民大选]]是在总理的「建议」下由总督发起，通常为四年一次，或在国会通过[[不信任动议|不信任动议]]后自动发起<ref>{{Cite web |title=Government and Canada's 41st Parliament: Questions and Answers |url=http://www.parl.gc.ca/Content/LOP/ResearchPublications/2011-37-e.htm |accessdate=2011-06-02 |author=O'Neal, Brian; Bédard, Michel; Spano, Sebastian |date=2011-04-11 |publisher=Library of Parliament |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110522071714/http://www.parl.gc.ca/Content/LOP/ResearchPublications/2011-37-e.htm |archivedate=2011-05-22 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。在上议院中的105位议员是从不同地区中选出，退休年龄为75岁<ref name="GriffithsNerenberg2003">{{Cite book |url=http://books.google.com/books?id=GytLtJacxY8C&pg=116 |title=Handbook of Federal Countries |last2=Karl Nerenberg |publisher=McGill-Queen's Press |year=2003 |page=116 |author1=Ann L. Griffiths |ISBN=978-0-7735-7047-4}}</ref>。获得次多下议院席位的党派的党魁会获得[[加拿大官方反对党主席|加拿大官方反对党主席]]的职位，该职位是议会系统的一部分，以防止政府不受制约<ref>{{Cite web |title=The Opposition in a Parliamentary System |url=http://www.parl.gc.ca/Content/LOP/researchpublications/bp47-e.htm |accessdate=2011-05-23 |publisher=Library of Parliament |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101125122354/http://www2.parl.gc.ca/content/lop/researchpublications/bp47-e.htm |archivedate=2010-11-25 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

在[[2015年加拿大國會下議院選舉|2015年的下议院选举]]中有五个政党被选入下议院，分别为：
* [[加拿大自由黨|加拿大自由黨]]（英語：{{lang|en|Liberal Party of Canada}}；法語：{{lang|fr|Parti libéral du Canada}}，中間派政黨,執政黨）
* [[加拿大保守黨|加拿大保守黨]]（英語：{{lang|en|Conservative Party of Canada}}；法語：{{lang|fr|Parti conservateur du Canada}}，中间偏右政黨,官方反對黨）
*[[新民主党_(加拿大)|新民主黨]]（英語：{{lang|en|New Democratic Party}}；法語：{{lang|fr|Nouveau Parti démocratique}}，社會民主主義的左翼政黨）
* [[魁人政團|魁人政團]]（法語：{{lang|fr|Bloc Québécois}}，主張[[魁北克獨立運動|魁北克獨立]]的政黨）
* [[加拿大綠黨|加拿大綠黨]]（英語：{{lang|en|Green Party of Canada}}；法語：{{lang|fr|Parti vert du Canada}}，環保主義政黨）

政府的责任被分为联邦政府部分和十个省的省政府部分。省议会实行[[一院制|一院制]]，运作方式与联邦议会相似<ref name="Montpetit" />。加拿大的三个地区也有各自的立法机构，但是相对于省，地区拥有的宪法权利较少，它们的结构也有不同<ref>{{Cite web |title=Differences from Provincial Governments |url=http://www.assembly.gov.nt.ca/visitors/what-consensus/differences-provincial-governments |accessdate=2014-01-30 |year=2008 |publisher=Legislative Assembly of the Northwest Territories |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140203044824/http://www.assembly.gov.nt.ca/visitors/what-consensus/differences-provincial-governments |archivedate=2014-02-03 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

=== 法律 ===
{{main|加拿大法律}}
加拿大的法律体系以普通法为主，部分地区如魁北克继承了法国的成文法传统。[[加拿大宪法|加拿大宪法]]为该国的最高法律，由成文法以及不成文惯例组成。在1867年通过的[[1867年英属北美法令|宪法法令]]划分联邦政府与省政府的权力。在1931年的《[[1931年西敏法令|西敏法令》]]使其在立法上有进一步的自主权，而在1982年通过的另一套{{Link-en|1982年宪法法令|Constitution Act,1982|宪法法令}}更令它在立法上完全独立，脱离英国的控制。那套法令同时修改原有的宪法，并加入《[[加拿大權利與自由憲章|加拿大權利與自由憲章]]》，这宪章保障加国公民的基本权利。通常政府不能凌驾这宪章，但是因{{Link-en|《加拿大人权利与自由宪章》第三十三条|Section Thirty-three of the Canadian Carter of Rights and Freedoms}}令联邦议会以及省议会有权利去推翻宪章的某些部分<ref>{{Cite book |title=Canadian Constitutional Law |url=https://archive.org/details/canadianconstitu0000unse_g6n7 |last=Bakan |first=Joel |publisher=Emond Montgomery Publications |year=2003 |isbn=978-1-55239-085-6 |pages=[https://archive.org/details/canadianconstitu0000unse_g6n7/page/3 3]–8, 683–687, 699 |coauthors=Elliot, Robin M}}</ref>。

[[File:Medal-Viki.jpg|thumb]]
虽然不是完全没有冲突，但早期欧洲人与原住民的交往都相对比较和平<ref name="Preston2009">{{Cite book |url=http://books.google.com/books?id=L-9N6-6UCnoC&pg=PA43 |title=The Texture of Contact: European and Indian Settler Communities on the Frontiers of Iroquoia, 1667-1783 |last=David L. Preston |publisher=U of Nebraska Press |year=2009 |pages=43–44 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150320194752/http://books.google.com/books?id=L-9N6-6UCnoC&pg=PA43 |archivedate=2015-03-20 |deadurl=no |ISBN=978-0-8032-2549-7 |access-date=2014-03-06 }}</ref>。在欧洲殖民时期初英国政府才开始正式与原住民进行外交。期后政府与原住民签署一系列条约和法律，例如{{link-en|印第安法令|Indian Act}}，令双方在争议上有规矩可言<ref name="FN">{{Cite journal |title=A First Nations - Federal Crown Political Accord, on the Recognition and Implementation of First Nation Governments |author=Assembly of First Nations, Elizabeth II |url=http://www.turtleisland.org/news/prekelowna.pdf |publisher=Assembly of First Nations |accessdate=2011-05-23 |year=2004 |series=1 |page=3 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5mNOfuTmo?url=http://www.afn.ca/cmslib/general/PolAcc.pdf |archivedate=2009-12-29 |deadurl=yes |ref=harv }}</ref>。其中最著名的{{Link-en|11项条约|Numbered Treaties}}，是由加拿大君主（[[维多利亚女王|维多利亚女王]]、[[爱德华七世|爱德华七世]]以及[[乔治五世_(英国)|乔治五世]]三位）与原住民在1871年至1921年之间所签署的一系列条约<ref name="Treaties">{{Cite web |title=Numbered Treaty Overview |url=http://www.canadiana.org/citm/specifique/numtreatyoverview_e.html |accessdate=2009-11-16 |work=Canadiana.org (Formerly Canadian Institute for Historical Microreproductions) |publisher=Canada in the Making |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100113201346/http://www.canadiana.org/citm/specifique/numtreatyoverview_e.html |archivedate=2010-01-13 |quote=The Numbered Treaties - also called the Land Cession or Post-Confederation Treaties - were signed between 1871 and 1921, and granted the federal government large tracts of land throughout the Prairies, Canadian North and Northwestern Ontario for white settlement and industrial use. In exchange for the land, Canada promised to give the Aboriginal peoples various items: cash, blankets, tools, farming supplies, and so on. The impact of these treaties can be still felt in modern times. |deadurl=no }}</ref>。这些条约是[[女王会同行政局|女王会同行政局]]与原住民制订，為[[加拿大原住民法律|加拿大原住民法律]]的基礎，由[[加拿大官方與原住民關係及北方事務部|加拿大官方與原住民關係及北方事務部]]监督實施。而{{Link-en|1982年宪法法令第三十五条|Section Thirty-five of the Constitution Act, 1982}}为这些条约提供进一步的保障<ref name="FN" />。原住民也受到这些条约保障，例如医疗保健，免税等优惠<ref name="Madison2000">{{Cite book |url=http://books.google.com/books?id=3AgrpoLkscMC&pg=PA128 |title=Is There a Canadian Philosophy?: Reflections on the Canadian Identity |last=Gary Brent Madison |publisher=University of Ottawa Press |year=2000 |page=128 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201114040134/https://books.google.com/books?id=3AgrpoLkscMC&pg=PA128 |archivedate=2020-11-14 |deadurl=no |ISBN=978-0-7766-0514-2 |access-date=2014-03-06 }}</ref>。

[[File:Ottawa_-_ON_-_Oberster_Gerichtshof_von_Kanada.jpg|thumb]]]]
加拿大的[[司法机关|司法机关]]有权解释法律和推翻议会的法案。 [[加拿大最高法院|加拿大最高法院]]的九位大法官是由总理和司法部推荐后由总督委任，并由首席大法官领导<ref>{{Cite book |title=Supreme at last: the evolution of the Supreme Court of Canada |url=https://archive.org/details/supremeatlastevo0000mcco |last=McCormick |first=Peter |publisher=James Lorimer & Company Ltd |year=2000 |pages=[https://archive.org/details/supremeatlastevo0000mcco/page/2 2], 86, 154 |ISBN=978-1-55028-692-2}}</ref>。所有高等法院和上诉法院的法官都是由联邦政府任命<ref name="YatesBain2000">{{Cite book |title=Introduction to law in Canada |url=https://archive.org/details/introductiontola00yate |last2=Penny Bain |last3=Ruth Yates |publisher=Prentice Hall Allyn and Bacon Canada |year=2000 |page=[https://archive.org/details/introductiontola00yate/page/93 93] |author1=Richard Yates |ISBN=978-0-13-792862-0}}</ref>。

加拿大大部分省份都實施[[英美法系|普通法]]，除了魁北克省，在那里是實施[[欧陆法系|歐陸法]]。联邦政府唯一一个能凌驾于其他省政府的法律是{{Link-en|加拿大刑事法律|Criminal law of Canada}}<ref>{{Cite book |title=An introduction to Canadian law |url=https://archive.org/details/introductiontoca0000swor |last=Sworden |first=Philip James |publisher=Emond Montgomery Publications |year=2006 |isbn=978-1-55239-145 -7 |pages=[https://archive.org/details/introductiontoca0000swor/page/22 22], 150}}</ref>。[[皇家加拿大騎警|皇家加拿大骑警]]可以在其他省份执法，虽然每个省都有自己的刑事法院和执法部门<ref>{{Cite web |title=Ontario Provincial Police |url=http://www.opp.ca/ecms/index.php?id=19 |accessdate=2012-10-24 |year=2009 |publisher=OPP official website |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121003163337/http://www.opp.ca/ecms/index.php?id=19 |archivedate=2012-10-03 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |title=Keeping Canada and Our Communities Safe and Secure |url=http://www.nbpei-ecn.ca/documents/ECN-Forensics.pdf |accessdate=2011-05-23 |last=Royal Canadian Mounted Police |publisher=Queen's Printer |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110706190335/http://www.nbpei-ecn.ca/documents/ECN-Forensics.pdf |archivedate=2011-07-06 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

加拿大法院包括联邦法院和省法院两套体系。联邦最高法院是最高审判机关。

=== 外交與軍事 ===
{{main|加拿大軍隊}}
[[File:Trudeau_visit_White_House_for_USMCA.jpg|thumb]]與美國總統[[唐納·川普|唐納·川普]]在[[白宮|白宮]]會面]]
加拿大现有75,000名常规自愿军以及约51,000名后备军人<ref>{{Cite web |title=Military Strength of Canada |url=http://www.globalfirepower.com/country-military-strength-detail.asp?country_id=Canada |accessdate=2014-02-11 |publisher=Global Firepower |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140222160358/http://www.globalfirepower.com/country-military-strength-detail.asp?country_id=Canada |archivedate=2014-02-22 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。[[加拿大軍隊|加拿大军队]]是由[[加拿大陸軍|加拿大陆军]]、[[加拿大皇家海军|加拿大皇家海军]]和[[加拿大皇家空軍|加拿大皇家空军]]组成。2011年，该国的军费开支大约为245亿[[加拿大元|加拿大元]]<ref>{{Cite web |title=Military expenditure of Canada |url=http://milexdata.sipri.org/result.php4 |accessdate=2012-05-03 |publisher=[[SIPRI|SIPRI]] |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120503052200/http://milexdata.sipri.org/result.php4 |archivedate=2012-05-03 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

加拿大与美国之间有着全世界最长的[[美加边境|不设防边境]]，而互相在军事方面也有着广泛的合作，且互为对方最大的贸易伙伴<ref>{{Cite journal |title=North American Cooperation in an Era of Homeland Security |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_orbis_fall-2003_47_4/page/675 |last=Haglung |first=David G |date=Autumn 2003 |journal=Orbis |publisher=Foreign Policy Research Institute |issue=4 |doi=10.1016/S0030-4387(03)00072-3 |volume=47 |pages=675–691}}</ref>。尽管如此，加拿大一直坚持着独立的外交政策，最显著的事件是坚持与[[古巴|古巴]]保持外交关系以及拒绝出兵[[伊拉克战争|伊拉克]]。作为[[英联邦|英联邦]]及[[法语国家及地区国际组织|法语圈国际组织]]成员，它与英国、法国以及前英法殖民地保持着密切的关系<ref>{{Cite book |title=Handbook of Canadian Foreign Policy |last=James |first=Patrick |publisher=Lexington Books |year=2006 |isbn=978-0-7391-1493-3 |editor-last=Michaud, Nelson; O'Reilly, Marc J |pages=213–214, 349–362}}</ref>。由于在二战中对解放荷兰作出重大贡献，它至今仍然与荷兰保持着良好的关系<ref name="netherlands" />。

由于与大英帝国及英联邦的紧密联系，加拿大参与许多由英国领导的军事行动，包括[[第二次布尔战争|第二次布尔战争]]及两次世界大战。自此以后，它便奉行多边主义，与其它国家合力解决世界问题<ref>{{Cite journal |title='Which Kind of Imperialism?' Early Cold War Decolonization and Canada–US Relations |url=http://utpjournals.metapress.com/content/24420698h63r2l2v/?genre=article&id=doi%3a10.3138%2fcras.37.3.403 |last=Teigrob |first=Robert |date=September 2010 |journal=Canadian Review of American Studies |issue=3 |doi=10.3138/cras.37.3.403 |volume=37 |pages=403–430 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140109095247/http://utpjournals.metapress.com/content/24420698h63r2l2v/?genre=article&id=doi%3a10.3138%2fcras.37.3.403 |archivedate=2014-01-09 |deadurl=yes |access-date=2014-06-08 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite book |title=Canada's international policy statement: a role of pride and influence in the world |publisher=Government of Canada |year=2005 |isbn=978-0-662-68608-8}}</ref>。它也是联合国和[[北大西洋公约组织|北大西洋公约组织]]的创始国之一。在[[冷战|冷战]]期间，加拿大是参与[[朝鲜战争|朝鲜战争]]的联合国成员之一，同时也与美国合作建立了[[北美空防司令部|北美空防司令部]]以防止苏联的空中袭击<ref>{{Cite book |title=Our lives: Canada after 1945 |url=https://archive.org/details/ourlivescanadaaf0000fink |last=Finkel |first=Alvin |publisher=Lorimer |year=1997 |isbn=978-1-55028 -551-2 |pages=[https://archive.org/details/ourlivescanadaaf0000fink/page/105 105]–107, 111–116}}</ref>。

[[File:US_Navy_090425-M-9917S-314_Canadian_Army_soldiers_assigned_to_Alpha_Company,_3d_Battalion,_22d_Regiment_of_Special_Purpose_Marine_Air_Ground_Task_Force-24_depart_a_U.S._Navy_landing_craft_air_cushion_(LCAC)_and_deploy_onto_Mayp.jpg|left]]在{{Link-en|UNITAS|UNITAS}}的軍事演習]]

在1956年的[[第二次中东战争|第二次中东战争]]中当时的对外事务国务部部长[[莱斯特·皮尔逊|莱斯特·皮尔逊]]（1963年当选加拿大总理）通过协调[[联合国维和部队|联合国维和部队]]介入战事以缓解紧张局面，因此他获得1957的[[诺贝尔和平奖|诺贝尔和平奖]]<ref>{{Cite book |url=http://books.google.com/books?id=MSHy65g7M7wC&pg=PA102 |title=Canadian foreign policy: defining the national interest |last=Holloway |first=Steven Kendall |publisher=University of Toronto Press |year=2006 |isbn=978-1-55111-816-1 |pages=102–103 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150320155924/http://books.google.com/books?id=MSHy65g7M7wC&pg=PA102 |archivedate=2015-03-20 |deadurl=no |access-date=2012-07-22 }}</ref>。因为这是联合国第一次执行维和行动，所以皮尔逊被经常认为是这种行动的开创人。由当时开始直到1989年，加拿大参与联合国的每一次维和行动，共50次<ref name="morton-milhist" />。加拿大也有在[[卢旺达|卢旺达]]和前[[南斯拉夫|南斯拉夫]]危机事件中派遣军事力量。但在向其它国家派遣军事力量时也会无法避免地引起一些争议，其中最大的一场争议为1993年的{{Link-en|索马里丑闻|Somalia Affair}}<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.nytimes.com/1994/11/27/world/torture-by-army-peacekeepers-in-somalia-shocks-canada.html |title=Torture by Army Peacekeepers in Somalia Shocks Canada |last=Farnsworth |first=Clyde H |date=1994-11-27 |newspaper=The New York Times |accessdate=2011-05-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110501200128/http://www.nytimes.com/1994/11/27/world/torture-by-army-peacekeepers-in-somalia-shocks-canada.html |archivedate=2011-05-01 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

1990年，加拿大加入了[[美洲国家组织|美洲国家组织]]，2000年7月在[[安大略|安大略]][[温莎_(安大略省)|温莎市]]举办了该组织的常务会议，2001年4月在魁北克市举行了第三次美洲国家峰会<ref>{{Cite web |title=Canada and the Organization of American States (OAS) |url=http://www.oas.org/en/member_states/member_state.asp?sCode=CAN |accessdate=2014-05-01 |publisher=Organization of American States |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140419222858/http://www.oas.org/en/member_states/member_state.asp?sCode=CAN |archivedate=2014-04-19 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。而为了与[[環太平洋地區|环太平洋地区]]的经济体有更紧密的关系，它也加入了[[亚洲太平洋经济合作组织|亚洲太平洋经济合作组织]]<ref name="Usaibp">{{Cite book |url=http://books.google.com/books?id=7jNg1U2tf6wC&pg=PA27 |title=Canada Intelligence, Security Activities and Operations Handbook Volume 1 Intelligence Service Organizations, Regulations, Activities |last=Ibp Usa |publisher=Int'l Business Publications |isbn=978-0-7397-1615-1 |page=27 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150320172246/http://books.google.com/books?id=7jNg1U2tf6wC&pg=PA27 |archivedate=2015-03-20 |deadurl=no |access-date=2014-03-06 }}</ref>。

[[File:HMCS_Regina_(FFH_334).jpg|thumb]]的[[哈利法克斯級巡防艦|哈利法克斯級巡防艦]]{{Link-en|里贾纳号|HMCS Regina}}]]
加拿大在联合国授权下派遣军队参与[[阿富汗战争_(2001年)|阿富汗战争]]，2011年7月开始撤军。在这场战争中，加国牺牲158名士兵、一名外交官、两名救助工作者和一名战地记者<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.ipolitics.ca/2013/09/27/canada-lost-afghan-war-says-author/ |title=Canada lost Afghan war, says author |author=Murray Brewster |date=2013-09-27 |publisher=Canada free press (iPOLOTICS) |accessdate=2012-01-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140221081753/http://www.ipolitics.ca/2013/09/27/canada-lost-afghan-war-says-author/ |archivedate=2014-02-21 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，并花费113亿加元<ref>{{Cite web |title=Cost of Afghanistan mission could reach $11.3B, government says |url=http://www.afghanistan.gc.ca/canada-afghanistan/news-nouvelles/2010/2010_07_09.aspx?lang=eng |accessdate=2014-06-08 |publisher=CBC news |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5uLgfkxeF?url=http://www.afghanistan.gc.ca/canada-afghanistan/news-nouvelles/2010/2010_07_09.aspx?lang=eng |archivedate=2010-11-19 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

2007年，该国与意大利、英国、[[挪威|挪威]]和俄罗斯一起宣布一项共十五亿美元的计划以支持发展中国家开发疫苗，并同时呼吁其它国家参与这项计划<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/02/06/idUSL06661675._CH_.2400 |title=Rich nations to sign $1.5 bln vaccine pact in Italy |last=Vagnoni |first=Giselda |date=2007-02-05 |publisher=Reuters |accessdate=2011-05-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110816205615/http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/02/06/idUSL06661675._CH_.2400 |archivedate=2011-08-16 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2007年8月，加国对{{Link-en|北极点的主权|Territorial claims in the Arctic}}受到俄罗斯的挑战，起因是俄罗斯在[[北极|北极]]进行了一次{{Link-en|2007年北极探险|Arktika 2007|深海考察}}，而加拿大自1925年起便打算将那一片地区纳入国土范围<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/1559165/Russia-claims-North-Pole-with-Arctic-flag-stunt.html |title=Russia claims North Pole with Arctic flag stunt |last=Blomfield |first=Adrian |date=2007-08-03 |newspaper=[[The_Daily_Telegraph|The Daily Telegraph]] |accessdate=2011-05-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110428173155/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/1559165/Russia-claims-North-Pole-with-Arctic-flag-stunt.html |archivedate=2011-04-28 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2011年3月至10月，在联合国的授权下，加拿大介入[[利比亞內戰_(2011年)|利比亚内战]]<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/story/2011/10/20/pol-libya-mission-end-two-weeks.html |title=Canada's Libya mission to end in 2 weeks |date=2011-10-20 |publisher=CBC |accessdate=2011-12-30 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111230170939/http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/story/2011/10/20/pol-libya-mission-end-two-weeks.html |archivedate=2011-12-30 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。從2014年开始，加拿大也在伊拉克部署了空軍和特种部队向[[伊斯兰国|伊斯兰国]]发动战争。

加拿大因其在国际事务上有一定程度的影响力，而被国际公认为[[中等強國|中等强国]]<ref name="Chapnick2011">{{Cite book |url=http://books.google.com/books?id=S2DPElbLK5sC&pg=PA2 |title=The Middle Power Project: Canada and the Founding of the United Nations |last=Adam Chapnick |publisher=UBC Press |year=2011 |isbn=978-0-7748-4049-1 |pages=2–5 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201104051632/https://books.google.com/books?id=S2DPElbLK5sC&pg=PA2 |archivedate=2020-11-04 |deadurl=no |access-date=2014-03-06 }}</ref>。除了是联合国，[[世界贸易组织|世界贸易组织]]和[[经济合作与发展组织|经济合作与发展组织]]等国际性组织的成员之外，它也是多个经济和文化组织的成员<ref>{{Cite web |title=International Organizations and Forums |url=http://www.international.gc.ca/cip-pic/organisations.aspx?lang=eng |accessdate=2014-03-03 |year=2013 |publisher=Foreign Affairs, Trade and Development Canada |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140227153935/http://www.international.gc.ca/cip-pic/organisations.aspx?lang=eng |archivedate=2014-02-27 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。1976年，加拿大签署并加入[[公民权利和政治权利国际公约|公民权利和政治权利国际公约]]<ref>{{Cite web |title=International Covenant on Civil and Political Rights |url=https://treaties.un.org/pages/viewdetails.aspx?src=treaty&mtdsg_no=iv-4&chapter=4&lang=en |accessdate=2014-03-03 |year=2014 |publisher=United Nations |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140306111401/https://treaties.un.org/pages/viewdetails.aspx?src=treaty&mtdsg_no=iv-4&chapter=4&lang=en |archivedate=2014-03-06 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

=== 行政區劃 ===
{{Main|加拿大行政區劃}}
加拿大是一个由十个省和三个地区组成的联邦。整个国家可分为四个主要区域：加拿大西部、加拿大中部、[[加拿大大西洋省份|大西洋省份]]以及加拿大北部。在[[医疗保险|医疗保险]]、[[教育|教育]]及[[社会福利|社会福利]]等方面，省通常比地区拥有较多自治权。各省的税收总合会比联邦政府多，这种政府架构在世界上是非常罕有。联邦政府可以在其他省份推行联邦法律，例如[[加拿大卫生法|加拿大卫生法]]，即使省政府可以选择不实行这些法律，但它们很少会这样做。联邦政府也有使用{{Link-en|均等支出|Equalization payments}}以确保每个省份都要付上相同的经济负担以换取相同的服务<ref>{{Cite web |title=Government Finance |url=http://www.statcan.gc.ca/pub/11-516-x/sectionh/4057752-eng.htm |accessdate=2011-05-23 |date=2008-10-22 |last=Bird |first=Richard M |work=Historical Statistics of Canada |publisher=Statistics Canada |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110610194706/http://www.statcan.gc.ca/pub/11-516-x/sectionh/4057752-eng.htm |archivedate=2011-06-10 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

