== 經濟 ==
{{main|加拿大经济}}
[[File:Canada_FTAs.png|thumb]]
[[加拿大銀行|加拿大银行]]为该国的[[中央银行|中央银行]]，由{{Link-en|斯蒂芬·朴洛兹|Stephen Poloz}}管理。[[加拿大財政部|财政部長]]和[[加拿大工業部|工业部長]]都会用[[加拿大統計局|加拿大统计局]]的数据来筹备财政计划。[[多伦多证券交易所|多伦多证券交易所]]是世界上第七大证券交易所，截至2012年，有1,577间公司在多伦多交易所上市。加拿大是[[各國國內生產總值列表_(國際匯率)|世界第10大经济体]]，2015年，它的[[国内生产总值|国内生产总值]]达1.550万亿美元<ref name=imf2 />。而它不但是经济合作与发展组织和八国集团的成员，它也是全球十大{{Link-en|貿易國|Trading nation}}之一，经济高度[[全球化|国际化]]<ref>{{Cite web |title=Latest release |url=http://www.wto.org/english/news_e/pres08_e/pr520_e.htm |accessdate=2011-05-23 |date=2008-04-17 |publisher=World Trade Organization |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/616iDeQXM?url=http://www.wto.org/english/news_e/pres08_e/pr520_e.htm |archivedate=2011-08-21 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |title=KOF Index of Globalization |url=http://globalization.kof.ethz.ch/maps/ |accessdate=2014-06-08 |publisher=KOF |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140927230247/http://globalization.kof.ethz.ch/maps/ |archivedate=2014-09-27 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。加拿大的经济为[[混合经济|混合经济]]，在[[美国传统基金会|美国传统基金会]]公布的[[经济自由度指数|经济自由指数]]中加国的排名高于美国和大部份西欧国家<ref>{{Cite web |title=Index of Economic Freedom |url=http://www.heritage.org/Index/ |accessdate=2013-06-27 |year=2013 |publisher=Heritage Foundation/''Wall Street Journal'' |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/616iEaYkN?url=http://www.heritage.org/Index/ |archivedate=2011-08-21 |deadurl=no }}</ref>，更经历过[[貧富差距|收入差距]]低于正常水平的时期<ref>{{Cite web |title=Jonathan Kay: The key to Canada's economic advantage over the United States? Less income inequality |url=http://fullcomment.nationalpost.com/2012/12/13/jonathan-kay-the-key-to-canadas-economic-advantage-over-the-united-states-less-income-inequality/ |accessdate=2012-12-14 |date=2012-12-13 |work=National Post}}{{dead link|date=2017年11月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。2008年，加拿大的进口额超过4429亿美元，其中价值2808亿美元的货品来自美国，117亿美元的货品来自日本和113亿美元的货品来自英国<ref name="import-export">{{Cite web |title=Imports, exports and trade balance of goods on a balance-of-payments basis, by country or country grouping |url=http://www40.statcan.gc.ca/l01/cst01/gblec02a-eng.htm |accessdate=2011-05-23 |date=2009-11-16 |publisher=Statistics Canada |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110428174031/http://www40.statcan.gc.ca/l01/cst01/gblec02a-eng.htm |archivedate=2011-04-28 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。2009年，它的[[贸易逆差|贸易逆差]]为48亿加元，相比2008年该国的贸易顺差为469亿加元<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.theglobeandmail.com/report-on-business/economy/canada-has-first-yearly-trade-deficit-since-1975/article1462607/ |title=Canada has first yearly trade deficit since 1975 |last=Grant |first=Tavia |date=2010-02-10 |newspaper=The Globe and Mail |accessdate=2011-05-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110428200530/http://www.theglobeandmail.com/report-on-business/economy/canada-has-first-yearly-trade-deficit-since-1975/article1462607/ |archivedate=2011-04-28 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

自20世纪初，当地的制造业，采矿业和服务业增长把加拿大从一个农业国家改造成一个工业化国家。与许多[[发达国家|发达国家]]一样，加拿大的经济以[[服务业|服务业]]为主，约四分之三的就业人口从事于该行业<ref>{{Cite web |title=Employment by Industry |url=http://www40.statcan.gc.ca/l01/cst01/econ40-eng.htm |accessdate=2011-05-23 |date=2009-01-08 |publisher=Statistics Canada |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110524063742/http://www40.statcan.gc.ca/l01/cst01/econ40-eng.htm |archivedate=2011-05-24 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。但在[[第一产业|一级产业]]方面它便与其它发达国家有所不同，加国的一级产业占当地经济相当大的比重，其中伐木和[[石油工业|石油工业]]更是该国两个十分重要的行业<ref>{{Cite journal |title=Recent Contributions to Economic History: Canada |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-economic-history_1995-03_55_1/page/98 |last=Easterbrook |first=WT |date=March 1995 |journal=Journal of Economic History |volume=19 |page=98}}</ref>。

加拿大是在发达国家中极少数的能源出口国之一<ref name="energy">{{Cite book |title=World energy resources |url=https://archive.org/details/worldenergyresou0000brow |last=Brown |first=Charles E |publisher=Springer |year=2002 |isbn=978-3-540-42634-9 |pages=[https://archive.org/details/worldenergyresou0000brow/page/323 323], 378–389}}</ref>。在大西洋省份的离岸区域储藏着丰富的[[天然气|天然气]]资源，而在艾伯塔省也储藏着大量石油及天然气资源，当地的{{Link-en|阿萨巴斯卡油田|Athabasca oil sands}}的巨大储量使加拿大拥有着全球约13%的[[石油儲量|石油储备]]，成为世界上第三大的石油储备国，仅次于[[委内瑞拉|委内瑞拉]]以及[[沙特阿拉伯|沙特阿拉伯]]<ref>{{Cite web |title=World proven crude oil reserves by country, 1960–2011 |url=http://www.opec.org/library/Annual%20Statistical%20Bulletin/interactive/current/FileZ/XL/T31.HTM |year=2012 |publisher=Organization of the Petroleum Exporting Countries |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130905210305/http://www.opec.org/library/Annual%20Statistical%20Bulletin/interactive/current/FileZ/XL/T31.HTM |archivedate=2013-09-05 |quote=Oil & Gas Journal's oil reserve estimate for Canada includes 5.392 billion barrels (857,300,000 m3) of conventional crude oil and condensate reserves and 173.2 billion barrels (2.754×1010 m3) of oil sands reserves. Information collated by [http://www.eia.doe.gov/emeu/international/oilreserves.html EIA] |deadurl=yes |access-date=2014-03-09 }}</ref>。加拿大是世界上其中一个最大的农产品出口国及矿产资源大国，它的大草原是世界上最重要的小麦，[[油菜|油菜]]以及其他谷物的产地之一<ref name="britton">{{Cite book |title=Canada and the Global Economy: The Geography of Structural and Technological Change |last=Britton |first=John NH |publisher=McGill-Queen's University Press |year=1996 |isbn=978-0-7735-1356-3 |pages=26–27, 155–163}}</ref>，而除了是[[锌|锌]]和[[铀|铀]]的主要出产国之外，它还大量出口[[金|金]]、[[镍|镍]]、[[铝|铝]]、[[钢材|钢材]]、[[铁矿石|铁矿石]]、[[焦炭|焦炭]]及[[铅|铅]]等矿产<ref name="energy" /><ref name="2009MineProduction">{{Cite web |title=Zinc Production by Country (Metric tons, zinc content of concentrate and direct shipping ore, unless otherwise specified) |url=http://www.indexmundi.com/minerals/?product=zinc&graph=production |accessdate=2012-05-14 |year=2009 |publisher=[[United_States_Geological_Survey|United States Geological Survey]] data via Index Mundi |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120601233256/http://www.indexmundi.com/minerals/?product=zinc&graph=production |archivedate=2012-06-01 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nrcan.gc.ca/minerals-metals/publications-reports/3264 |title=Mineral Trade {{!}} Natural Resources Canada |accessdate=2014-03-09 |archive-date=2013-11-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131120005127/http://www.nrcan.gc.ca/minerals-metals/publications-reports/3264 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。许多气候恶劣的北部城市正是靠着附近的矿产和木材资源维持生计。在南部，特别是安大略省以及魁北克省两省的南部，制造业十分发达，汽车与[[飛行器|飛行器]]製造业是当地两大重要产业<ref>{{Cite web |title=Vl-12 |url=http://www.statcan.gc.ca/pub/11-516-x/sectionv/4057758-eng.htm#V332_350 |accessdate=2011-05-23 |year=1983 |publisher=Statistics Canada |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/616iH9b2U?url=http://www.statcan.gc.ca/pub/11-516-x/sectionv/4057758-eng.htm#V332_350 |archivedate=2011-08-21 |editor=Leacy, FH |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

[[File:Nafta.jpg|left]]]]
自第二次世界大战以后，加拿大与美国的经济联系愈来愈紧密。在1965年签署的{{Link-en|美加汽车产品贸易协定|Canada-United States Automotive Products Agreement}}打通两国之间的汽车制造工业的贸易边境。在20世纪70年代，能源危机爆发以及担心外资掌控着国家的制造业，促使总理[[皮埃尔·特鲁多|皮埃尔·特鲁多]]的自由党政府制订{{Link-en|国家能源计划|National Energy Program}}和外国人投资审查机构<ref>{{Cite book |url=http://books.google.com/books?id=q4gt2xhqpSIC&pg=PA50 |title=Governance, multinationals, and growth |last=Morck |first=Randall |publisher=Edward Elgar Publishing |year=2005 |isbn=978-1-84376-909-5 |page=50 |chapter=Who owns whom? Economic nationalism and family controlled pyramidal groups in Canada |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201204001236/https://books.google.com/books?id=q4gt2xhqpSIC&pg=PA50 |archivedate=2020-12-04 |deadurl=no |coauthors=Tian, Gloria; Yeung, Bernard |editors=Eden, Lorraine; Dobson, Wendy |access-date=2012-07-22 }}</ref>。但在20世纪80年代，进步保守党总理[[马丁·布赖恩·马尔罗尼|马丁·布赖恩·马尔罗尼]]废除国家能源计划并将后者改名为{{Link-en|加拿大投资|Investment Canada}}，以鼓励外资到加拿大进行投资<ref>{{Cite journal |title=The Dog That Hasn't Barked: The Political Economy of Contemporary Debates on Canadian Foreign Investment Policies |last=Hale |first=Geoffrey |date=October 2008 |journal=Canadian Journal of Political Science |issue=3 |doi=10.1017/S0008423908080785 |volume=41 |pages=719–747}}</ref>。1988年，加拿大与美国签署的[[北美自由贸易协议|美加自由贸易协定]]消除两国之间的关税，而于1994年美加自由贸易协定扩展为[[北美自由贸易协议|北美自由贸易协定]]，将自由贸易区扩展至[[墨西哥|墨西哥]]<ref name="britton" />。在90年代中期，自由党总理[[让·克雷蒂安|让·克雷蒂安]]开始紧缩开支，逐步还清国家债务<ref name="Johnson2006">{{Cite book |url=http://books.google.com/books?id=TcL80sSautgC&pg=PA374 |title=Thinking Government: Public Sector Management in Canada |last=David Johnson |publisher=University of Toronto Press |year=2006 |isbn=978-1-55111-779-9 |page=374 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201124105419/https://books.google.com/books?id=TcL80sSautgC&pg=PA374 |archivedate=2020-11-24 |deadurl=no |access-date=2014-03-09 }}</ref>。

2008年，[[次贷危机|次贷危机]]波及至加拿大并导致[[经济大衰退|经济大衰退]]，令失业率上升<ref>{{Cite web |title=Jobless rate to peak at 10%: TD |url=http://www.nationalpost.com/related/topics/story.html?id=1383376 |accessdate=2011-05-23 |date=2009-03-13 |last=Sturgeon |first=Jamie |work=National Post |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5nDiwjKnX?url=http://www.nationalpost.com/related/topics/story.html?id=1383376 |archivedate=2010-02-01 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。2009年10月，加国全国的失业率达8.6％，但各省之間的失業率懸殊，從失业率只有5.6%的马尼托巴省（全国最低）到最高的紐芬蘭與拉布拉多失业率高达17%<ref>{{Cite web |title=Latest release from Labour Force Survey |url=http://www.statcan.gc.ca/subjects-sujets/labour-travail/lfs-epa/lfs-epa-eng.htm |accessdate=2011-05-23 |date=2009-11-06 |publisher=Statistics Canada |archive-date=2011-08-21 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/616iFcdMK?url=http://www.statcan.gc.ca/subjects-sujets/labour-travail/lfs-epa/lfs-epa-eng.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2008年到2010年之间，该国减少16万全职工作岗位和22万永久职位<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.theglobeandmail.com/report-on-business/economy/economy-lab/the-economists/the-real-state-of-canadas-jobs-market/article1757129/ |title=The real state of Canada's jobs market |last=Yalnizyan |first=Armine |date=2010-10-15 |newspaper=The Globe and Mail |accessdate=2010-12-12 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101230070221/http://www.theglobeandmail.com/report-on-business/economy/economy-lab/the-economists/the-real-state-of-canadas-jobs-market/article1757129/ |archivedate=2010-12-30 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2010-2011财政年，加拿大的{{Link-en|加拿大联邦债务|Canadian public debt|联邦债务}}为5567亿美元，相比于2008－2009财政年的4637亿美元加国的债务有所增长<ref>{{Cite web |title=Budget fights deficit with freeze on future spending |url=http://toronto.ctv.ca/servlet/an/local/CTVNews/20100304/budget_2010_100304/20100304?hub=TorontoNewHome |accessdate=2011-05-23 |date=2010-03-04 |publisher=CTV News |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110428195933/http://toronto.ctv.ca/servlet/an/local/CTVNews/20100304/budget_2010_100304/20100304?hub=TorontoNewHome |archivedate=2011-04-28 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。此外，加拿大的[[外债|外债]]在2010年第一季度從410亿美元上升至1940亿美元<ref>{{Cite web |title=Canada's international investment position |url=http://www.statcan.gc.ca/daily-quotidien/100617/dq100617b-eng.htm |accessdate=2011-05-23 |date=2010-06-17 |work=The Daily |publisher=Statistics Canada |archive-date=2017-10-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171005065339/http://www.statcan.gc.ca/daily-quotidien/100617/dq100617b-eng.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。但是，由於该国较保守的银行体系以及政府在金融危机前有财政盈余和实行已久的调低国债政策，使其受经济大衰退的影响比其他八国集团成员国少<ref>{{Cite web |title=Canada's Budget Triumph |url=http://mercatus.org/publication/canada-s-budget-triumph |accessdate=2013-07-15 |date=2010-09-30 |format=PDF |publisher=Mercatus Center (George Mason University) |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130814181403/http://mercatus.org/publication/canada-s-budget-triumph |archivedate=2013-08-14 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。2013年，整体上加拿大的经济已稳定下来，但它依然被经济增长放缓，[[歐洲主權債務危機|欧债危机]]以及失业率高企等问题困扰<ref>{{Cite web |title=Update of Economic and Fiscal Projections |url=http://www.fin.gc.ca/efp-pef/2013/efp-pef-02-eng.asp |accessdate=2014-02-11 |year=2013 |publisher=Department of Finance Canada |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140222064604/http://www.fin.gc.ca/efp-pef/2013/efp-pef-02-eng.asp |archivedate=2014-02-22 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。与此同时，联邦政府和当地许多产业开始将贸易扩展至新兴亚洲市场，尝试使加拿大出口多元化。2011年，亚洲是加拿大第二大的出口市场，仅次于美国<ref>{{Cite web |title=Canada's Trade with the World, by Region |url=http://www.asiapacific.ca/statistics/trade/regional-trade/canadas-trade-world-region |accessdate=2013-01-09 |date=2012-03-22 |publisher=Asia Pacific Foundation of Canada |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130114221917/http://www.asiapacific.ca/statistics/trade/regional-trade/canadas-trade-world-region |archivedate=2013-01-14 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |title=Minister Fast Congratulates the Organizers of the Canada and Free Trade with Asia Conference |url=http://opencanada.org/branch-news/montreal-news/minister-fast-congratulates-the-organizers-of-the-canada-and-free-trade-with-asia-conference/ |accessdate=2014-02-11 |year=2013 |publisher=Canadian International Council |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140222060205/http://opencanada.org/branch-news/montreal-news/minister-fast-congratulates-the-organizers-of-the-canada-and-free-trade-with-asia-conference/ |archivedate=2014-02-22 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。但是，为了增加出口石油到中国而建议兴建的{{Link-en|恩桥北关输油管道|Enbridge Northern Gateway Pipelines}}引起广泛争议<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.theglobeandmail.com/globe-investor/investment-ideas/streetwise/northern-gateway-pipeline-would-strengthen-trade-ties-to-china/article4107144/ |title=Northern Gateway pipeline would strengthen trade ties to China |date=2012-05-07 |work=The Globe and Mail |accessdate=2012-08-19}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |title=Pipeline economics: China needs oil, and Canada's got it |url=http://www2.macleans.ca/2012/09/25/plugging-for-pipelines/ |accessdate=2012-12-04 |date=2012-09-25 |publisher=Macleans.ca |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121203020207/http://www2.macleans.ca/2012/09/25/plugging-for-pipelines/ |archivedate=2012-12-03 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

== 科技 ==
[[File:STS-116_Payload_(NASA_S116-E-05364).jpg|thumb]]上的[[加拿大机械臂|加拿大机械臂]]帮发现号执行[[STS-116|STS-116]]任务]]
2011年，加拿大投入大约299亿加元用作[[研究开发|研究开发]]<ref>{{Cite web |title=Spending on research and development |url=http://www.statcan.gc.ca/daily-quotidien/120113/dq120113d-eng.htm |accessdate=2012-04-29 |date=2012-01-13 |publisher=Statistics Canada |archive-date=2012-05-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120510162925/http://www.statcan.gc.ca/daily-quotidien/120113/dq120113d-eng.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。截至2012年，加拿大在[[诺贝尔物理学奖|物理]]，[[诺贝尔化学奖|化学]]和[[诺贝尔医学奖|医学]]方面培育14位[[諾貝爾獎得主列表|诺贝尔奖得主]]，并同年在一个有关科学家的大型国际调查中在科研质量方面名列全球第四<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/national/canada-ranked-fourth-in-the-world-for-scientific-research/article4571162/ |title=Canada ranked fourth in the world for scientific research |date=2012-09-26 |work=[[The_Globe_and_Mail|The Globe and Mail]] |accessdate=2012-10-17 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121004001349/http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/national/canada-ranked-fourth-in-the-world-for-scientific-research/article4571162/ |archivedate=2012-10-04 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。加拿大也有许多国际性的高科技公司<ref>{{Cite web |title=Top 250 Canadian Technology Companies |url=http://www.branham300.com/index.php?year=2011&listing=1 |accessdate=2012-01-13 |publisher=Branham Group Inc |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111219061504/http://www.branham300.com/index.php?year=2011&listing=1 |archivedate=2011-12-19 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。该国在[[各国互联网使用者数目列表|各国互联网使用者数目]]上排行第17位，有超过2840万名用户，相等于2012年其总人口的83％<ref>{{Cite web |title=Internet Usage and Population in North America |url=http://www.internetworldstats.com/stats14.htm#north |accessdate=2012-12-20 |date=June 2012 data |publisher=Internetworldstats |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121224045307/http://www.internetworldstats.com/stats14.htm#north |archivedate=2012-12-24 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

[[加拿大太空局|加拿大太空局]]对[[航天机构列表|探索太空计划]]十分积极，例如外太空，行星和航空技术研究以及发展火箭和卫星科技。1962年，当{{Link-en|云雀1号|Alouette 1}}成功升空之后，加拿大便成为第三个能自行研发，建造和发射人造卫星到太空的国家，仅次于[[苏联|苏联]]和美国<ref>{{Cite web |title=Alouette I and II |url=http://www.asc-csa.gc.ca/eng/satellites/alouette.asp |accessdate=2012-11-30 |publisher=CSA |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6AADm2L2d?url=http://www.asc-csa.gc.ca/eng/satellites/alouette.asp |archivedate=2012-08-24 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。1984年，[[馬克·加諾|馬克·加諾]]成为该国第一位太空人。2013年，加拿大共有9位太空人曾进入太空，参加超过十五次载人飞行任务<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/technology/story/2010/09/01/f-canadian-space-astronauts.html |title=Canada's astronauts |date=2010-10-26 |publisher=CBC News |accessdate=2011-12-08 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120110132132/http://www.cbc.ca/news/technology/story/2010/09/01/f-canadian-space-astronauts.html |archivedate=2012-01-10 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

加拿大参加兴建[[国际空间站|国际空间站]]的计划，并是太空[[机器人|机器人]]技术的先驱，它为国际空间站和美国国家航空航天局的航天飞机建造[[加拿大臂|加拿大臂]]，[[移动维修系统|加拿大臂2号]]和{{Link-en|特克斯特号|Dextre}}三个机械人。自1960年，加国的航天科技公司为商业市场设计和制造多种型号的卫星，例如{{Link-en|RADARSAT1号|Radarsat-1}}和{{Link-en|2号|Radarsat-2}}，[[ISIS卫星|ISIS卫星]]以及{{Link-en|MOST卫星|Microvariability and Oscillations of STars telescope}}等<ref>{{Cite web |title=The Canadian Aerospace Industry praises the federal government for recognizing Space as a strategic capability for Canada |url=http://www.newswire.ca/en/releases/archive/March2010/11/c9200.html |accessdate=2011-05-23 |publisher=Newswire |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110609224813/http://www.newswire.ca/en/releases/archive/March2010/11/c9200.html |archivedate=2011-06-09 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。它同时也成功研发和制造一些被广泛使用的[[探空火箭|探空火箭]]，例如{{Link-en|黑布兰特|Black Brant}}，自它在1961年推出之后已被使用超过一千次<ref>{{Cite web |title=Black Brant Sounding Rockets |url=http://www.bristol.ca/BlackBrant.html |accessdate=2011-05-23 |publisher=Magellan Aerospace |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111027024026/http://www.bristol.ca/BlackBrant.html |archivedate=2011-10-27 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

