}}</ref>。该国的移民主要是来自中国，菲律宾和印度<ref>{{Cite web |title=Canadians want immigration shakeup |url=http://cnews.canoe.ca/CNEWS/Politics/2010/11/09/16054896.html |accessdate=2010-11-14 |last=Lilley |first=Brian |year=2010 |work=Parliamentary Bureau |publisher=Canadian Online Explorer |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101110203045/http://cnews.canoe.ca/CNEWS/Politics/2010/11/09/16054896.html |archivedate=2010-11-10 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。根据加拿大统计局的数字，在2031年加拿大的有色人种少数裔群将会占其总人口的三分之一<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/national/the-changing-face-of-canada-booming-minority-populations-by-2031/article1494651/ |title=The changing face of Canada: booming minority populations by 2031 |last=Friesen |first=Joe |date=2010-03-09 |newspaper=The Globe and Mail |accessdate=2012-05-14 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120516192348/http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/national/the-changing-face-of-canada-booming-minority-populations-by-2031/article1494651/ |archivedate=2012-05-16 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，這將會跟今日的美國相似。

加拿大是世界上[[各国移民数列表|移民率最高的国家]]之一<ref>{{Cite book |url=http://books.google.com/books?id=kv4nlSWLT8UC&pg=PA51 |title=Canada |last=Zimmerman |first=Karla (2008) |publisher=Lonely Planet Publications |isbn=978-1-74104-571-0 |edition=10th |page=51 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121112164223/http://books.google.com/books?id=kv4nlSWLT8UC&pg=PA51 |archivedate=2012-11-12 |deadurl=no}}</ref>，主因是受该国的{{Link-en|经济政策对移民加拿大的影响|Economic impact of immigration to Canada|经济政策}}和[[家庭移民政策|家庭移民政策]]影响。2012年，有257,887人移民至加国<ref>{{Cite web |title=Facts and figures 2012 – Immigration overview: Permanent and temporary residents |url=http://www.cic.gc.ca/english/resources/statistics/facts2012/permanent/01.asp |accessdate=2014-05-01 |date=2013-08-07 |publisher=Citizenship and Immigration Canada |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140502011322/http://www.cic.gc.ca/english/resources/statistics/facts2012/permanent/01.asp |archivedate=2014-05-02 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。大多数新移民都会生活在多伦多，蒙特利尔和温哥华等主要城市<ref name="Grubel2009">{{Cite book |url=http://books.google.com/books?id=48LOyfxYihoC&pg=PA5 |title=The Effects of Mass Immigration on Canadian Living Standards and Society |last=Herbert G. Grubel(2009) |publisher=The Fraser Institute |isbn=978-0-88975-246-7 |page=5 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200920133252/https://books.google.com/books?id=48LOyfxYihoC&pg=PA5 |archivedate=2020-09-20 |deadurl=no |access-date=2014-03-18 }}</ref>。加拿大也接受大量[[难民|难民]]<ref>{{Cite web |title=Refugees in Canada |url=http://www.cic.gc.ca/english/refugees/?_ga=1.113463047.1687779032.1391414351 |accessdate=2014-05-01 |date=2013-08-23 |publisher=Citizenship and Immigration Canada |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140502011324/http://www.cic.gc.ca/english/refugees/?_ga=1.113463047.1687779032.1391414351 |archivedate=2014-05-02 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，它所接受的难民占全球难民数量的10%以上<ref name="Simmons2010">{{Cite book |url=http://books.google.com/books?id=K0YwAJ7MpswC&pg=PA92 |title=Immigration and Canada: Global and Transnational Perspectives |last=Alan Simmons(2010) |publisher=-{Canadian Scholars’ Press}- |isbn=978-1-55130-362-8 |page=92 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140627175242/http://books.google.com/books?id=K0YwAJ7MpswC&pg=PA92 |archivedate=2014-06-27 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。
加拿大約有140萬原住民，佔總人口的4%，主要包括「第一民族」（First Nations）、因紐特人（Inuit）和梅蒂人（Métis）；其中第一民族人數最多，約85萬人，實際上就是加拿大的「印地安人」。近年來加拿大的極具爭議的原住民人權逐漸受到關注，成為該國面對其歷史錯誤的一部份，加拿大仍在對這部分黑暗的過去進行揭露和反思<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-57997867 |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-07-31 |archive-date=2021-08-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210811073923/https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-57997867 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
